#: ../../source/modules/configuration/authentication/imap.rst:2
msgid "Authenticate from IMAP"
msgstr "Autenticar a partir do IMAP"

#: ../../source/modules/configuration/authentication/imap.rst:4
msgid ""
"The interfacing of GLPI with mail servers as a source of authentication."
msgstr ""
"A interface do GLPI com servidores de e-mail como fonte de autenticação."

#: ../../source/modules/configuration/authentication/imap.rst:6
msgid ""
"This authentication source is configured from the menu Configuration > "
"Authentication > Mail servers."
msgstr ""
"Esta fonte de autenticação é configurada no menu Configurar > Autenticação >"
" Servidores de e-mail."

#: ../../source/modules/configuration/authentication/imap.rst:8
msgid ""
"This ability can compensate for the absence of directory or of CAS server. "
"However, contrary to what is possible with other sources of other "
"authentication sources, no mass import is available. A user is authenticated"
" by GLPI if the server of mail server has authenticated him beforehand."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/modules/configuration/authentication/imap.rst:12
msgid ""
"The connection to the mail server uses the IMAP or POP protocols. The "
"options of SSL and TLS encryption are available. The distinction is made "
"between the mail domain which is the part of the of the mail address that "
"follows the asterisk character, and the fully qualified name of the mail "
"server, which can serve several mail domains."
msgstr ""
